9|access-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209010912/https://www.gamerankings.com/switch/245046-windjammers/index.html|archive-date=2019-12-09|url-status=live}}</ref><br />(PS4) 78.94%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamerankings.com/ps4/202547-windjammers/index.html|title=Windjammers for PlayStation 4|work=[[GameRankings]]|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]|date=2019|access-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209013143/https://www.gamerankings.com/ps4/202547-windjammers/index.html|archive-date=2019-12-09|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|JXV       = (PS4/PSV) 14 / 20<ref name=\"Jv.comPS4PSVw\">{{cite web|author=akazan|url=http://www.jeuxvideo.com/test/706902/windjammers-un-depoussierage-dans-le-vent.htm|title=Test de Windjammers par jeuxvideo.com|work=[[Jeuxvideo.com]]|publisher=[[FIMALAC#Divisions|Webedia]]|date=September 10, 2017|access-date=2020-04-23|language=fr}}</ref>\n|NLife     = (Switch) {{Rating|8|10}}<ref name=\"NLifeNSw\">{{cite web|last=Lopes|first=Gon\u00e7alo|url=http://www.nintendolife.com/reviews/switch-eshop/windjammers|title=Windjammers Review (Switch eShop) - Insert disc to play|work=[[Nintendo Life]]|publisher=Nlife Media|date=October 23, 2018|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>\n|rev1      = ''[[:de:M! Games|MAN!AC]]''\n|rev1Score = (PS4) 75 / 100<ref name=\"M!PS4w\">{{cite web|last=Steppberger|first=Ulrich|url=https://www.maniac.de/tests/windjammers-im-test-ps4/|title=Top Hunter \u2013 im Test (PS4)|work=[[:de:M! Games|MAN!AC]]|publisher=Cybermedia|date=October 1, 2017|access-date=2020-24-23|lang=de}}</ref>\n|rev2      = ''Video Chums''\n|rev2Score = (PS4) 7.0 / 10<ref name=\"VChumsPS4w\">{{cite web|last=Palmer|first=Stephen|url=https://videochums.com/review/windjammers|title=Windjammers Review - The original disc thrower whizzes onto PlayStation|website=videochums.com|publisher=Video Chums|date=September 10, 2017|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>\n}}\n\nVideo game website [[Giant Bomb]] began regularly playing the game on camera in 2013, eventually giving it their \"Old Game of the Year\" award.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.giantbomb.com/articles/giant-bomb-s-2013-game-of-the-year-awards-day-one/1100-4803/|title=Giant Bomb's 2013 Game of the Year Awards: Day One|work=[[Giant Bomb]]|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]|date=December 23, 2013|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref> The same website later classified the game as a runner-up for \"2017's Old Game of the Year\" at the Game of the Year 2017 Awards.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.giantbomb.com/articles/game-of-the-year-2017-day-one-old-disappointing-sh/1100-5699/|title=Game of the Year 2017 Day One: Old, Disappointing, Shopkeepers, and Looks|work=[[Giant Bomb]]|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]|date=December 25, 2017|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>\n\nThe game has also enjoyed a resurgence in popularity thanks to a growing competitive scene. In 2018, it appeared at the [[Evolution Championship Series|Evolution Championship Series (EVO)]] annual fighting game championships in Las Vegas as a side tournament.<ref name=\"Dw\">{{cite web|last=Moyse|first=Chris|url=https://www.destructoid.com/windjammers-has-one-of-the-highest-number-of-entrants-at-animevo-2018-514870.phtml|title=Windjammers has one of the highest number of entrants at AnimEVO 2018 - Beats out KoF XIV, BlazBlue and Garou|work=[[Destructoid]]|publisher=[[Enthusiast Gaming]]|date=July 30, 2018|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>\n\n{{clear}}\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://gamefaqs.gamespot.com/arcade/564208-windjammers ''Windjammers''] at [[GameFAQs]]\n* [https://www.giantbomb.com/windjammers/3030-11500/ ''Windjammers''] at [[Giant Bomb]]\n* [https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=10441 ''Windjammers''] at [[Killer List of Videogames]]\n* [https://www.mobygames.com/game/windjammers ''Windjammers''] at [[MobyGames]]\n\n{{Neo Geo}}\n{{Portal bar|1990s|Japan|Video games}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Windjam