ara operation (1920)|Bukhara operation]]).\n|-\n|[[File:Bandera de Khiva 1917-1920.svg|31px|border]]\n|[[Khanate of Khiva|Khiva <small>(Uzbekistan)</small>]]\n|Abdallah Khan\n|Monarchy deposed by a communist uprising aided by the Red Army ([[Khivan Revolution]]).\n|-\n|[[File:Flag of Kingdom of Syria (1920-03-08 to 1920-07-24).svg|31px|border]]\n|[[Arab Kingdom of Syria|Syria]]\n|[[Faisal I of Syria|Faisal I]]\n|Monarchy deposed, following the [[Siege of Damascus (1920)|Siege of Damascus]].\n|-\n|[[File:Ottoman Flag.svg|31px|border]]\n|[[Ottoman Empire]]\n|[[Mehmed VI]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"|1922\n|[[Abolition of the Ottoman Sultanate|Sultanate abolished]] in 1922.\n|-\n|\n|[[Wituland]]\n|Fumo `Umar ibn Ahmad\n|rowspan=\"1\"|1923\n|Sultanate abolished by [[British Empire|British]], the country was incorporated into [[Kenya Colony]].\n|-\n|[[File:Hellenic Kingdom Flag 1935.svg|31px|border]]\n|[[Kingdom of Greece (Gl\u00fccksburg)|Greece]]\n|[[George II of Greece|George II]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|1924\n|Restored 1935 and later abolished again in 1973 (see below).\n|-\n|[[File:Flag of Bogd Khaanate Mongolia.svg|31px|border]]\n|[[Bogd Khaanate of Mongolia|Mongolia]]\n|[[Bogd Khan]]\n|Communist [[Mongolian People's Republic|People's Republic]] proclaimed after Khan's death.\n|-\n|[[File:Albania 1914 Flag.svg|31px|border]]\n|[[Principality of Albania|Albania]]\n|[[William I, Prince of Albania|William I]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"|1925\n|Monarchy restored in 1928 ([[Kingdom of Albania (1928\u201339)|Albanian Kingdom]]).\n|-\n|\n|[[Mohammerah]]\n|[[Khaz'al al-Ka'bi]]\n|1925\n|Sheikhdom abolished by [[Persia]]\n|-\n|\n|[[Kingdom of Orungu|Orungu]]\n|Rogomb\u00e9-Nw\u00e8ntchandi\n|1927\n|Position abolished by [[French Third Republic|French]].\n|-\n!colspan=\"6\" style=\"background:#eeeeaa;\"|1930s\n|-\n|[[File:Flag of Spain (1785-1873 and 1875-1931).svg|31px|border]]\n|[[Spain under the Restoration|Spain]]\n|[[Alfonso XIII of Spain|Alfonso XIII]]\n|1931\n|Later restored (see below).\n|-\n|\n|[[Ki